Mary Magdalene</em> was guaranteed and had an irrevocable bid, but still ma=
naged to outrun the $2 million estimate to make $3.12 million.<br/><br/></p=
><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">At Christie=E2=80=99s, <strong>Jo=
